September 1, 2018
For me, I knew it was important that Makhai was not only a part of our special day, but I made it a point to ask him first if I had his blessings to be his Daddy’s girlfriend. Mak replied with so much excitement, a very big YES! I made him promise not to say anything and that night at the A’s fireworks show…we made it official with Makhai by our side while fireworks lit up the sky 🎉 It was a truly magical moment. This picture was taken that very night! 
HAPPY 6 YEAR ANNIVERSARY! 
Thank you and Makhai for lighting up my world!!! 😘
